For both controls and PD subjects, cortical parcellation and subcortical  segmentation were performed on co -registered T1 images with the default reconstruction  pipeline of Freesurfer  image analysis suite by using the Desikan -Killiany  atlas 20, which is  documented and freely available for download online 21 (http://surfer.nmr.mgh.harvard.edu/ ).
